source: This money is what my sister could saved from her internship term and lend me to keep in crypto dollar form to protect against extreme devaluation of Turkish Lira together with inflation of USD. Turkish lira lost so much value last year so this was very important for her to cover her nearly 2 months of living costs next year since she will be in another city alone for education.
